{"tid":1321001,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"侮辱好過見血！","createTime":"2019-07-15T14:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T14:43:15.000Z","uid":10521,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"85d5fe42debf52639c2859979e9ae2d85da6d583","tid":1321001,"uid":10521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:13:50.000Z","msg":"住嗰度呢排成日一班狗係街口度吠，又亂鳩咁咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得捉狗來講，鈍器就好過利器，識少少關節技就最好，佢哋啲皮咁厚，要瞄準皮薄嘅位好難，但係成隻腳咁扭會易捉好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋如果見血，佢行動力未必會下降，但係其他狗見到就會更有藉口發癲，左鄰右里見到又有嘢講，話你虐畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然噴到佢哋咩都睇唔到就最快，一個人都可以噴幾隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於捉到之後，佢哋啲皮通常都深色，就幫佢哋噴啲鮮艷啲嘅色，紅色就幾好，又搶眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8078e34f02e37381229088e52334acfbd469a380","tid":1321001,"uid":10521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:19:28.000Z","msg":"仲有，啲狗隻腳咁俾你扭一扭，下次出唔出到黎吠都成問題，但係割傷佢分分鐘有仆街幫佢包一包下次又出嚟咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5374abf7f0219e3a12c8a2dd298532a3364314","tid":1321001,"uid":10521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:21:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a95cb6de0b1fa0db23a82ee468e6a79b32022ea","tid":1321001,"uid":10521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5bDNmrFraBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5bDNmrFraBA&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=0b553534\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5bDNmrFraBA</a><br />\n其實所謂關節技學啲最簡單嘅就得，一捉到四肢，向外逆時針咁轉一圈就乜都斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />技巧就係一捉到即刻扭，俾佢察覺到你想扭佢，佢啲四肢用力，就會陷入鬥力嘅局面，切記要速戰速決，捉到嗰下扭唔到就退"},{"pid":"ef8cd7e09ba9a2149c9a884d4b53f5a21d77cf84","tid":1321001,"uid":10521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:27:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5b9ad65f25262cf1acb380400ffb3bb6b694dc","tid":1321001,"uid":10521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:27:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374cf48ada30615bd6e320463c5002d041cea3cc","tid":1321001,"uid":10521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:28:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608d5ae3796e8add8a5c16f31e5d93ce4b8a94ed","tid":1321001,"uid":10521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:28:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a63b7de378f858a20a2a1a38b70ff9d3fc465c","tid":1321001,"uid":10521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051ec54b25da546c27c2b9e94d7e3e681ad05566","tid":1321001,"uid":10521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed198a42e08e024f70149675163bba6a560a98e9","tid":1321001,"uid":10521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2023aae673e295a64d1a08af892908e8b0c17011","tid":1321001,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f9ebaaa3efbe89734ccc77e44600fb94c24d588d","tid":1321001,"uid":10521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:31:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0b29b394fd1c37d9cb802ccfad07b5306d5fdaa2","tid":1321001,"uid":10521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor